provenance/010-household-decision-protocol/03-close.md:86:- **The Outsider's four concrete outcome-shaping contributions are visible in the artefact's surface text.** Move 4's burden-cost asymmetry clause ("caring more doesn't automatically beat ongoing burden"), the hybrid second-person/first-person-example voice, the title "A House Decision in Five Moves", and the individually-addressable-moves structural feature are all Outsider-originated. A future reader auditing OI-004 closure criterion 3 could trace each of these four back to `01c-perspective-outsider.md` and confirm the chain-of-provenance.
