specifications/workspace-structure-v4.md:202:6. Check that each directory in `applications/` corresponds to an external artefact produced or regularized in a session whose decision record in provenance authorises its presence
specifications/workspace-structure-v4.md:203:7. Check that every external artefact file in `applications/` carries the `originating_session` frontmatter field; for regularized artefacts, also `regularized_in_session` and `provenance_witness_path`
