specifications/identity.md:49:- **Durability by construction.** The woven edge keeps the cloth from fraying. The methodology's preservation discipline — v1/v2/v3 files, explicit `supersedes`/`superseded-by` pointers, provenance as a first-class output — keeps prior reasoning from being lost even as the methodology evolves.
