provenance/015-session-assessment/00-assessment.md:47:**Where the close is right.** In-session Validate findings *do* trigger Cell 2 iteration — this is a genuine mitigation of the validation-to-Produce feedback concern *within a session*. Cell 2 does preserve within-session iteration between its internal Produce rounds.
