1 words) archive-packed at `provenance/022-workspace-scaling-trajectory/archive/014-oi016-outsider/`; R8c' Session 022's own Outsider raw (22,611 words) archive-packed at session close. Mempalace R3 `CLAUDE.md` paragraph removed per E.1 (Session 020 §5.4 warrant trigger 1 satisfied; not engine-definition). Engine-v3 is the first engine-v-bump to introduce a new engine-definition spec file (beyond the original eleven at v1).
