:7** (required catches up with voluntary; first session-since-014 with even ratio). **NOVEL DATA PATTERN at Session 021**: Outsider performed pre-response workspace exploration (four `exec` tool calls reading specifications/engine-manifest.md, multi-agent-deliberation.md, open-issues.md, provenance/017/, provenance/020/) before producing its response body. This grounded the response in actual spec text rather than the brief's quoted excerpts; per Outsider's own honest-limits this did not violate §10 anti-import (workspace read is not pretraining import). Recorded for future OI-015 / criterion-4 deliberations on the boundary between brief content and workspace context for Outsider perspectives.
