provenance/044-session-assessment/02-decisions.md:81:The substantive MAD v4 amendment proposed in `01-deliberation.md` §3.2 (the (d)-class lineage-constrained-role formulation preferred by 3-of-4 cross-family including both non-Claude perspectives) is **not adopted this session**. Adoption is **deferred to Session 047 or later**, pending D-133 M2 verification-window evidence.
